OL,3,CLondon bus crashes into home in
OL,4,CNotting Hill
OL,6,FEmergency services were called to a
OL,7,Fhome in Notting Hill, after a London
OL,8,Fbus crashed into the front of it.
OL,10,FMetropolitan Police officers received
OL,11,Freports of a collision on St Quintin
OL,12,FAvenue shortly after 7pm on Thursday 2
OL,13,FJuly.
OL,15,FThey attended along with crews from
OL,16,Fthe London Ambulance Service and
OL,17,FLondon Fire Brigade.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
