OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1783691326
OL,3,CLondon bus crashes into home in
OL,4,CNotting Hill
OL,6,FAccording to the force no injuries
OL,7,Fwere reported, no arrests have been
OL,8,Fmade, and no criminal offences have
OL,9,Fbeen identified.
OL,11,FLondon Ambulance Service sent a
OL,12,Fparamedic in fast response car to the
OL,13,Fscene but no one needed treatment.
OL,15,FKensington and Chelsea Council said it
OL,16,Fis aware of the incident and officers
OL,17,Fremain on site.
OL,19,FIt said dangerous structure engineers
OL,20,Fare assessing the damage.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
