OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1783691326
OL,3,CLondon bus crashes into home in
OL,4,CNotting Hill
OL,6,FCllr Johnny Thalassites, lead member
OL,7,Ffor resident services, planning and
OL,8,Fenforcement, said: "We'd expect an
OL,9,Finvestigation to be underway to
OL,10,Festablish the cause, but we're just
OL,11,Fglad nobody appears to be seriously
OL,12,Fhurt."
OL,14,FThe Met Police are asking anyone with
OL,15,Finformation to call 101 quoting CAD
OL,16,F7570/2July.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/4
