OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1783691326
OL,3,CLondon bus crashes into home in
OL,4,CNotting Hill
OL,6,FTransport for London said, "A route 70
OL,7,Fbus was involved in a collision
OL,8,Fyesterday. There was a minor injury
OL,9,Fthat thankfully did not require
OL,10,Ftreatment.
OL,12,F"The safety of our customers,
OL,13,Fcolleagues and members of the public
OL,14,Fis of paramount importance, and we are
OL,15,Fworking closely with the bus operator,
OL,16,FFirst Bus, who are investigating this
OL,17,Fincident."
